<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2013-09-03</DATELINE><TITLE>Introduction: The World of Bats</TITLE><BODY>Bats are unique flying mammalians that occur worldwide feeding either on insects, fruits or even on blood depending on the species. Since they are active during the night, many myths have been launched during the last 500 years. All these facets are shortly considered here and prepare for a hopefully intense look into their hidden life.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>